[normal]The partnership is a case study of good practice[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]“The programme has had a measurable effect on the problem [of illicit tobacco] in the North of England.  It was the first programme to develop a comprehensive approach to tackling the demand for and the supply of illicit tobacco… The scheme is an exemplar of partnership working and should now be widely disseminated.”
